Version:     CVS
System:      any
Severity:    minor
Problem:
	It needs to be automated.
Code:
Transcript:
Comments:
Fix:
	You can now use ml96/Bugs/new to carve out bug reports.
	For example,
		./Bugs/new 'something is broken in TILT'
	will carve out a new bug report with the given description.
